Required Software Versions
    * gtkmm development package version 3.4 or newer
    * cairomm development package version 1.10 or newer
    * g++ >= 4.7 or clang++ >= 3.0

Testsystems:
    * Fedora 18 64bit, cairomm-devel 1.10, gtkmm30-devel 3.6, clang++ 3.2, g++ 4.7.2
    * Debian Wheezy 64bit, libcairomm-1.0-dev 1.10, libgtkmm-3.0-dev 3.4, clang++ 3.0, g++ 4.7.2


Building with clang:
    CXX=clang++ make -j4
or for the debug version:
    CXX=clang++ make -j4 debug


Building with g++:
    CXX=g++ make -j4
or for the debug version:
    CXX=g++ make -j4 debug

Executing the Jpeg-Decoder:
./jpgd data/sample1.jpg    
